

* Installation

  Clone the =org-mode= Github repository into =~/.emacs.d/lisp=. Then make autoloads.

  #+BEGIN_SRC sh
    cd ~/.emacs.d/lisp/
    git clone git@code.orgmode.org:bzg/org-mode.git
    cd org-mode/
    make autoloads
  #+END_SRC

  Next, in the =init.el= file, add the =org-mode= to the =load-path=

  #+BEGIN_SRC emacs-lisp
    (add-to-list 'load-path "~/.emacs.d/lisp/org-mode/lisp")
    (add-to-list 'load-path "~/.emacs.d/lisp/org-mode/contrib/lisp" t)
  #+END_SRC
